war powers clause and resolution in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Grenada</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Lebanon</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Libya</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Central America</ENAMEX>,
