<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">tiller</ENAMEX>. As <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Reagan</ENAMEX> said, "You can't have <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">535</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">secretaries</ENAMEX> of <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE_DESC">state</ENAMEX>."

